There are two baseball fields at the Pits . The large and main venue is in the northeast corner of the park . The field has limited seating capacity with bench seats along the first and third bases with most spectators sitting along the grass hills . A wood broadcast booth is located at the top of the northeast corner . There are no change rooms at this field , players change in the washrooms near the concession stand beyond centre field . A smaller baseball diamond is located next to the washroom facilities . 